data.description: Built in 2023 Chesmar home lived in for less than a year. In the newly popular Las Lomas community on the outskirts of Forney and close to lots of shopping. The popular one-story Raleigh plan is finished out with the 4th bedroom and 3rd full bath option, as well as an oversized 2.5 car garage.  Owner transferring for work.  Updated entry lighting, cabinet pulls throughout, ceiling fans in all bedrooms.  All secondary bedrooms large enough to hold king size bed (floorpan in pics). Huge island kitchen with lots of cabinet space.  Layout of home was very well thought out.
